Bruker du DVD+R eller DVD-R?

DVD-R tar 4,489 MB mens DVD+R bare tar 4,483 MB, men jeg vet ikke hvor stor ISO-filen er?

Great torrent! But remember, it will only burn using DVD-R, it will not fit on DVD+R discs.

This is caused by small differences in capacity between the two:

DVD+R = 4,700,000,000 bytes
DVD-R = 4,707,000,000 bytes

This image = 4,703,784,960 bytes, so it's in between.
